@fahmi_fadzil There is no fiber in the village. Have to use wireless 4G broadband. The price is crazy expensive Maxis unlimited RM135.

Digi, celcom and others cannot be used because the network is very bad.

It has been decades and there has been no significant change. Even Maxis has a bad line and has reported the same MCMC many times.

@XavierNaxa That's what I mean. I think it's 5G Yes, it's really fast.
But in terms of overall coverage, Maxis is indeed the best compared to Digi and Celcom.
If not for this reason, I would have switched to another telco a long time ago. Maxis is expensive, but worth what you pay.
